<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;+&nbsp;SCP-3932</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;-&nbsp;The&nbsp;Dolphin&nbsp;Manifesto</a></div>
